          <h2 class="top-margin"><span>6. Send</span> your invoices with Freshbooks</h2>
          <p>
            Freshbooks is the perfect accounting tool for non-accountants. Creating invoices can be a huge hassle if you lack experience in bookkeeping - luckily, Freshbooks has stripped invoicing down to it’s core components, in a simple UI that’s guaranteed to save you hours upon hours on accounting work.
          </p>
